@stats
Feature: Share group statistics

Ability for groups to embed widgets that highlight their achievements
in their own websites.

The host is presented with a basic piece of HTML which will pull in 
statistics when it is embedded into a website.

The two statistics available for embedding are:

- headline stats
- CO2 equivalence visualisation

